==[[Noun]]==
===etymology===
Acronym from '''ra'''dio '''d'''etection '''a'''nd '''r'''anging.

===meanings===
#A system to detect aircraft, ships and other objects in a certain area. It uses pulses of high frequency electromagnetic waves.  It is similar to [[sonar]], which uses sound instead of radio waves.

